data.description: Don't miss this 3 bedroom, 2 bath in great Ringgold location! Zoned for Heritage schools! Spacious living area with vaulted ceiling greets you and flows into kitchen / dining area for great family times and easy entertaining. Master bedroom has its own private bath with lots of counter space. Two additional bedrooms for the kiddos or guests.. Laundry room is conveniently located in the hall near the bedrooms. There is plenty of space in the unfinished basement for future expansion or lots of storage. Outside is a covered front porch for lazy afternoons and a deck in back for those summer cookouts. House is being sold as-is. With some updating and repairs you would have amazing home! Call today for a showing. At this price, it won't last long!
